public/fallback-*.js
public/fallback-*.js.map

# Vitest
.vitest

# Security & Backups
SECURITY_*.md
backups/
*.sql
*.sql.gz
DISASTER_RECOVERY_PLAN.md

# MCP Servers - Credentials
../mcp-servers/*/.env
!../mcp-servers/*/.env.example

